22
00:01:11,000 --> 00:01:14,000
Yep. Acidic, all right.

23
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:18,000
Oh, thank God.

24
00:01:18,000 --> 00:01:19,000
Excuse me?

25
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:22,000
I'm so sorry, Dwight, and if you want me to be there,

26
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:24,000
