27
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:27,000
I just have a personal training session.

28
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:29,000
Okay, that's tough.

29
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:34,000
I get red dirt. Nobody is getting red dirt.

30
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:36,000
I should have kept my mouth shut.

31
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:39,000
We're not even that close. I've only known Dwight 12 years.

32
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:44,000
12 years. Time is a son of a bitch.

33
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:51,000
I'm sure she's in a better place.

34
00:01:51,000 --> 00:01:53,000
I really hope so.

35
00:01:57,000 --> 00:02:01,000
Okay, now this is crazy. You can't make a dirt ball...

36
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:03,000
I miss her so much.

37
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:04,000
Okay.

38
00:02:04,000 --> 00:02:06,000
You know?

39
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:09,000
Ah!

40
00:02:27,000 --> 00:02:32,000
There's a bright golden haze on the meadow,

41
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:36,000
a bright golden haze on the meadow.

42
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:41,000
Zeke's here.

43
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:42,000
Zeke!

44
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:45,000
Hey, Dwight. Mellow's mom says hi.

45
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:47,000
Hi to mom.

46
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:49,000
You going?

47
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:51,000
Will there be ghosts there?

48
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:54,000
Get in the sidecar.

49
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:56,000
Get in the sidecar.

50
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:58,000
You get in the sidecar!

51
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:06,000
What are you doing here?

52
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:09,000
You invited me. You threw the red dirt in my face.

53
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:11,000
Oh, yeah.

54
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:13,000
Who is that?

55
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:15,000
Jeb, my brother.

56
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:16,000
You have a brother?

57
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:18,000
You invited me to come with you.

58
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:19,000
Jeb, my brother.

59
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:21,000
You have a brother.

60
00:03:21,000 --> 00:03:24,000
I didn't really see a better parking spot.

61
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:25,000
Oh!

62
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:27,000
Look what I did.

63
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:31,000
That's a rental.

64
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:38,000
You want to go in?

65
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:39,000
No, you want to go in?

66
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:40,000
You want to go in?

67
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:41,000
I'll put you in there.

68
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:42,000
Okay, I'll put you in there.

69
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:43,000
